{"tid":1375457,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向港共發動經濟戰","createTime":"2019-07-28T05:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:11:08.000Z","uid":32511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff30ed0d1e41cc47d9609925bb55686976a065c","tid":1375457,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFuWD5F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFuWD5F.png&h=7d599999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先上表顯示，港共收入主要來源為利得稅，印花稅，地價收入，同其他收入如博彩稅<br />\n<br />\n利得稅：所有野儘量幫趁小企業，上Amazon同樂天買野。<br />\n<br />\n印花稅：唔買港股，或買免印花稅產品，或美股/ADR。二手樓已冇咩成交，儘量打擊一手樓銷售，重點係令佢賣唔出。工商物業成交亦會因經濟轉差減少。<br />\n<br />\n地價：經濟差，投地出價會傾向保守。間接打擊收入<br />\n<br />\n其他收入：主要指博彩稅。外地巴打嘅話，波同馬可以考慮除馬會以外嘅渠道。<br />\n<br />\n針對港共人士商業活動：做生意嘅就拒絕幫趁，服務業嘅轉搵其他人接手。"},{"pid":"235cfc05358eae48a136044122495f96c580f71c","tid":1375457,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJdPY9i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJdPY9i.png&h=54fb92df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少左波同馬都幾係野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec240c77f942c7b2d50982905760fb2c0607242","tid":1375457,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:32:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22a2867ac575cc08c9bf1db7a017c9b638d8e68f","tid":1375457,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:33:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"252ee51a5f4d87cad9ed044332ef38b38fc545aa","tid":1375457,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:47:40.000Z","msg":"換美金cash out/放離岸戶口好過"},{"pid":"9389bc2f6e2479291d33c5a4100169c7aa877a34","tid":1375457,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,